[With the emergence of sleeping sickness in the neighbouring countries
Tanzania, Uganda and the Democratic Republic Congo, it is not
surprising that sleeping sickness is also being experienced in Rwanda.
As pointed out in the message, rigorous vector control is as important
as ever. - Mod.EP
